{"tid":310383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭進場！大部份泛民站立恭迎聖駕！","createTime":"2017-07-05T18:10:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-05T18:50:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fcf69afcaec1bfa52fb0f99b21086c09f0605528","tid":310383,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T18:10:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170705/s00001/ae0c7e47ac8f88ad07332bda5e9d11cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170705%2Fs00001%2Fae0c7e47ac8f88ad07332bda5e9d11cf.jpg&h=62a774fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民主黨主席胡志偉亦說，林鄭月娥由當選至今，一直展示希望盡最大努力，修補行政立法關係，他們站立是為了展示立法會及廣大市民對林鄭月娥的期望。他表示，會對林鄭月娥持觀望態度，看她是否能在未來政策倡議上廣納不同意見，而民主派暫時採取「聽其言、觀其行」態度。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯主席李慧琼讚賞林鄭月娥在首次答問會表現不錯，認為林鄭月娥熟悉政策。她又說，林鄭月娥上任後首次立法會大會就到場，顯示她重視行政立法關係，而部分非建制派議員在林鄭月娥進場、離場時站立顯示禮貌，是好的開始。<br />\n<br />\n議員田北辰形容林鄭月娥表現不過不失。公民黨立法會議員楊岳橋則認為，林鄭月娥仍迴避尖銳政治問題，預示新政府沒有足夠能力和決心解決這些問題。"},{"pid":"4743281c2088ab1c83e520bbda58c71e1ea0bac2","tid":310383,"uid":51022,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T18:18:32.000Z","msg":"禮貌黎，有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81258baa2d54e6e86a72f1af839d054f52fd7c19","tid":310383,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T18:30:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>禮貌黎，有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://imgs.ntdtv.com/pic/2014/10-13/p5461512a374844382.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimgs.ntdtv.com%2Fpic%2F2014%2F10-13%2Fp5461512a374844382.jpg&h=fef820fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5d7b09d5fe757b446eabc49f5c6fd1d0022a618e","tid":310383,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T18:50:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>禮貌黎，有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"ht